NAMESPACE_COMMON_XML::XmlSaxContext* XmlDeserializable::GetSaxContext (   ) 
 

Gets the SAX context to pass to the GisXmlSaxHandler callbacks. Classes derived from FdoXmlDeserializable can override this function to specify a SAX context with class-specific information.

Returns:
Returns NULL by default, the default NAMESPACE_COMMON_XML::XmlSaxContext is used. The default provides basic error handling functionality.
